Shakedown Street-> Minglewood Blues-> It Must Have Been The Roses, Little Red Rooster, Althea, Me & My Uncle-> Mexicali Blues, Good Time Blues, Cumberland Blues-> Looks Like Rain-> Might As Well

Set 2

reviews.review_text:
Not bad at all I love going to " This just in " and listening to the new versions released of show have listened to for years. My theory is they have been redone with all the new tech software .  
 I love the sound of this Tour empty halls and our garage band still Grateful Dead. This is a very good sounding aud, I love it....
